<h2>Why You Need This (But Don't Know It Yet)</h2>
<p>Building a sleep stack from scratch is overwhelming — there are hundreds of products, each claiming to be the missing piece. The real issue isn't finding one good sleep product; it's finding three that work together. Most people either settle for a single solution (one pillow, one mask, one spray) or get stuck researching for weeks. This bundle solves decision fatigue by pre-curating three complementary products that address the three key sleep senses.</p>
