<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is the Deep Sleep Bundle?</h2>
<p>The Deep Sleep Bundle combines three best-selling sleep products into one cohesive system. You get the Bluetooth Sleep Mask (flat speakers, blackout, side-sleeper friendly), the Restnature White Noise Machine (16 sounds, 32 volume levels), and the Serene Sleep Spray (lavender/chamomile/sandalwood). It's designed for people building a complete sleep environment from zero — not for someone who already owns sleep gadgets. Together, these three products address the neurological pathways to sleep: audio, ambient sound, and aromatherapy.</p>

